## Best Practices
- Set explicit timeout for every external API request.
- Wrap remote API calls in try/catch and propagate actionable errors.
- Keep credentials in environment variables only; never hardcode secrets.
- Validate structured vision/message payload before sending.
- Use bounded retries where remote provider instability is expected.

